snippet.description:
This is the story of a young Nepali youth who leaves his home, family, and village to chase small dreams in a foreign land. But will those dreams come true? Or will fate write a different ending? A journey filled with hope, struggle, and silence and a truth that reveals itself only at the end. Watch till the last moment. some stories don‚Äôt end, they stay in your heart forever.

snippet.description:
‚ÄúRatna‚Äù is a cherished Nepal Bhasa classic, originally written and created by the legendary Bishnu Jalmi and Krishna Man Dangol, and immortalized by the soulful voice of Juju Kaji Ranjit.
With utmost respect to the original creators, and inspired by the heartfelt reinterpretation by Raju Maharjan & Kutumba, we humbly present our small tribute to Ratna ‚Äî a sincere attempt to honor its heritage, express our gratitude, and celebrate the timeless soul of Newa music. 

Inspired By : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oc6vKrJdjtA 

The Team
Music Produced & Directed by - @ShreejanShyamaa 
Music Coordinated by - Bishal Basi
Sung by - Priya Basnet
Filmed by - Sujan Sujakhu & Sujal Suwal
Percussions - Sudin Lachhimasyu & Sudeep Chawal
Flute - Shrijan Maharjan

snippet.title: Bipul Chettri - Prakriti (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Life as we know it, is a multitude of experiences, a passage of time, where we face bouts of happiness and sadness while moving along. We often join the rat race and forget to live life as a journey while we keep deferring our happiness. Bipul‚Äôs ‚ÄòPrakriti‚Äô (nature) is a reflection of an escape from this rat race that we find ourselves in while ignoring aspects of nature that functions as a metaphor of life, things and people in our lives, we take for granted.

Musicians

Bipul Chettri - Guitars, Vocals, Backing Vocals
Pranai Gurung - Guitars
Rahul Rai ‚Äì Bass

snippet.title: Shaky ( Official #Video ) Sanju Rathod Ft. Isha Malviya | G-Spark | New #Marathi Songs 2025
snippet.description:
Provided To Youtube By Amal Star Media
| üïâ ||
Sanju Rathod presents 'Shaky' a Marathi track like no other!

Shaky is a fresh Marathi Pop anthem that blends playful Afrobeat grooves with everyday desi charm. Sanju Rathod and Isha Malviya bring effortless swag, catchy hooks, and vibrant energy in this fun, feel-good love track. A bold, danceable vibe that pushes Marathi music into exciting new territory.

Singer - Sanju Rathod
LyricsComposer - Sanju Rathod
Music Produced By - G-Spark
